Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it look?! Have we lost them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they've given \Nup. I can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.62,0:01:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that monstrous\Ncannon sure scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck were they hiding that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cannon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you know, that huge thing\Nthat the warriors were carrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, that"?! Hey, it's no laughing\Nmatter! It was really scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! There they are! It's Nami and Conis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Nami-san!! Conis-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you all right?!\N--Of course!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Off to the Blue Sea!! \NFinale Woven by Feelings"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? They rushed off of the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We couldn't even give them our gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How disappointing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they even realize how\Nmuch we appreciate what they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:03:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. They have no idea how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair, Aisa... that you alone\Ngot to say goodbye to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's in an uproar that\Nwe let our saviors run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Luffy and the others\Ntold me not to tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say anything to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I said, "Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Laki, did you know?\NLuffy's body stretches!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd be like, "Gum-Gum Pistol!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aisa, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know there was a strong\Nwarrior like him in the Blue Sea, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be like him, like "Gum-Gum...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just trim your hair\Nfor today. Let your hair grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll look good on you.\NYou're a girl, so you should look cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute?! Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... since there won't be\Nany need for you kids to carry arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and since you can now live freely,\Nlike people in the sky should.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're ladylike today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, don't move, Aisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ladylike Laki!\N--Aisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Warrior Calgara...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were told that the Shandians'\Nrole had been fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure your wish was delivered\Nto your best friend as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We no longer have to make\Nfuture generations shed blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:05:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle is over...\Nbut we won't lose our pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please continue to watch over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We swear that we will not let the\Nfire of Shandora go out ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Sky Knight,\Na freelance soldier-for-hire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This land won't need such a thing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What this land needs now\Nis someone to govern it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that I'd like \Nyou to be that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the best suited for it. This city\Nbelonged to your people from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all of a sudden?\NThat's not a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this battle, I think\Neveryone must have realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that no one can own Vearth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"God" is our support.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the land is Skypiea.\NThe name of the city is Shandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only person who can unify them is you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who continued to be anguished\Nby the battle in this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Knight Gan Fall... I would like\Nyou to take the seat of God again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and support this land \Nwhose scar is still deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like you to, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gan Fall-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--If it's you, we'll accept it, too!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Gan Fall!\N--God!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I thought I could finally\Nreally enjoy growing pumpkins...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! We can see it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look to the front! It's Cloud End!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Let's see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So we can go back down from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got here sooner than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going back down, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, now that we're about to\Ngo back, I admit I hate to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to say goodbye\Nto this pure white sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky island was fun... \Nthough it was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So once we go through that gate,\Nwe'll be heading straight down
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Blue Sea via a Milky Road, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we can visit \Nthe sky island again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to tell with this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, everyone! I'm sorry!\NWe'll say goodbye here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for seeing us off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis-chan! Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say hello to the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we should be thanking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis, old guy and little\Nwhite one! You all take care!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, furl the sails immediately\Nand hold on tight to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Do as the old guy said!\NSounds like it's gonna go pretty fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're sliding from a\N7,000-meter height! Hurry up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:09:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says, "Don't forget about me."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... That's the South Bird\Nwe brought to the sky with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Captain! We got\Nthe log for the next island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Once we get off from here,\Nwe'll start on a new adventure again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! You ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go back to the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Be careful while dropping!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:10:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While dropping?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heso!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! The sky island's\Nfamous Octopus Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an octopus!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow-ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! This is so cool!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've slowed down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I thought that I was finally\Ngonna go to the netherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring it! See off the saviors of\Nthis land by ringing the bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heso!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! See you again!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come visit us again!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to the Blue Sea safely!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you look up, you see the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this God's Land on the\Nclouds a dream or reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10,000 meters far up in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you listen carefully, you can\Nhear the sound of the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It rings today, and it \Nwill ring again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the bell that echoes in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,glorifies and sings about \Nthe wandering land...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! This feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're calling off the search?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just natural, right?!\NThe city of gold was in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't find anything\Nat the bottom of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Old-timer...\N--Old-timer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really thank you all... for joining\Nme to pursue my dream for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat us like strangers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of romanticism\Nshall we go after next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Noland the Liar"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll follow you to the ends\Nof the earth, old-timer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold! Gold! Gold! Gold! Gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've finally become super rich!!\NWhat shall we buy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about buying a huge bronze statue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron! What's the point of\Nexchanging gold with bronze?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should increase the number of\Ncannons! Let's buy ten of them! Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! I want a lockable refrigerator!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't be stupid! What're we gonna\Ndo when we get hungry?! I object!\N--I... I... I want you to buy me some books!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I want to read medical\Nbooks from other countries!!\N--That's just why we should buy it, you dumb ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on a second, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll split the treasure once\Nwe get back down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please buy books for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we buy whatever you guys like, I have\Na feeling that it won't do us any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navigator...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where this ship is heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? The next island...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?! What?!\N--What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! We started riding an air current\Nat some point and now we're drifting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Air current?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, there is a wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is! As it stands, we don't\Nknow where on the sea we'll land!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do? In this state,\NI can't set the sails and control the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry. We'll just head back\Nto the next island once we reach the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just blurt things out \Ncasually, as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Sanji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I guess it was my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a problem! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm gonna cut you into fillets,\Nyou damn Moss Head!\N--You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Zoro's tired, too,\Nafter the battle in the sky, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's completely set now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a nice view.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Is it morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said that the sun set!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's taking quite a long time\Nto get to the Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so worried about how \Nfar the ship will drift.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall I sing a love song or\Nsomething to take your mind off it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be quick and easy if we\Ndrifted to Raftel, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! That'd be cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get to Raftel, we still have to go more\Nthan halfway around the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well, yeah... I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'm so bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When are we gonna reach the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're bored, come here,\Ntoo, Zoro! This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did his voice come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounded sorta far off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over here! Everyone, come up here, too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! So he is up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! This is awesome!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't be reckless!\NOur lives depend on that balloon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Luffy! Come back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Luffy, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter all of a sudden, Sanji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This octopus is shrinking!\NIf we don't do anything, we'll fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He said this octopus is shrinking!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,\Nit looks smaller than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do?!\NWe're still pretty high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it'll last \Nuntil we reach the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:18:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Luffy! Something is strange,\Nso come back down!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite a scare, since\Nit stopped bouncing suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, the octopus is shrinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh? I didn't do anything,\Nbut we came back to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! We're falling! We're falling!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! At this rate,\Nwe'll be swallowed by the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no guarantee\Nthat we'll fall into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! That's right! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else?! Protecting the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be reckless, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:19:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp Aa-aa-aa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use all the Breath Dials I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Float!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's slowed down.\N--Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were we saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see my wonderful work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered what was gonna\Nhappen for a moment there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, seriously, I thought that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, grab onto something and hold tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Robin-chan! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That startled me! The octopus\Nsuddenly shrunk all the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the air leaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we somehow made\Nit down... without dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we really went to an\Nincredible place, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've fallen, it's so far up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if we were dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dream land. I wonder if\Nwe can go visit again some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might be able to get closer if you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, so you think you can go to heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, things're calm now at any rate.\NI'll make coffee or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather have dinner, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying I'll get on it right away,\Nso have some coffee and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck... are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling lonely, talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gaze at the heavens\Nas you wander about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the moon,\Nyou keep your gaze constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your deep reflection wanes\Nas you slowly disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as you are, let those words guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream, you travelers who spend\Ncountless nights drifting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you may not be able to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will surely start moving forward again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:22:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! Where are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.25,0:22:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these spotlights?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A stage?! Is it my one-man show?!\N--Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the siren for a state of\Nemergency! Could this place be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, it looks like we've\Nfallen to a damn troublesome place!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we'd better\Nfirst get away from the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What about dinner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.93,0:23:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.23,0:23:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A State of Emergency Is Issued!\NA Notorious Pirate Ship Has Infiltrated!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.73,0:23:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
